credit_line: Gift of Stephen W. Brener and Carol B. Brener
title: "Scribner's Magazine"
provenance: Collection of Carol B. Brener and Stephen W. Brener
description:
Rectangular, with beige and black enameled front resembling the cover of a January issue of Scribner's Magazine. The right long side has incised, vertical lines intended to resemble pages. Reverse is undecorated except for the inscription "W.W. Hallock." Lid hinged on left. Striker of incised hatch marks on bottom. 

Sterling 2867
name: Matchsafe
